request.description:
Invokes the FX Qualification workflow using the **RestClient** implementation.

🎯 **This request triggers ALL Prometheus metrics:**
- fxqual_workflow_duration_ms
- fxqual_step_duration_ms{step="customer"}
- fxqual_step_duration_ms{step="promo"}
- fxqual_step_duration_ms{step="product"}
- fxqual_step_duration_ms{step="fxInterest"}
- fxqual_method_invocations_total
- fxqual_quotes_requested_total
- fxqual_quotes_qualified_total

After executing this request, open:
👉 http://localhost:8080/actuator/prometheus
and search for `fxqual_` to see your workflow + step metrics.
